### Test Import/Export Functionality
### This file can be used with REST Client extensions in VS Code or similar tools

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Export Students as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=students&format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Export Consultations as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=consultations&format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Export Notes as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=notes&format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Export Students as JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=students&format=json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Import Students from CSV
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

